summary: Make your classic city style change more fantasy
descriptionHtml:
I hope everyone like this mod it just for beautiful landscape i don't have time to discover the script if i have free time i will release portal to where you like to jump.
This mod will add some element that make all city and town in skyrim look pretty.
Still miss some city i will update soon.
You can find 2 dawnbreaker sword with special enchant near a well at falkreath gate.
It no need marker, it on every cities and town in skyrim map.
Recommend Dawnguard and Dragonborn DLC.
Put it in data folder (first need extract rar)
I very thank you who watch this mod.
author: Black Art
